definitions.definition: ( Internet ) A website that allows users to reflect, share opinions, and discuss various topics in the form of an online journal, sometimes letting readers comment on their posts . Most blogs are written in a slightly informal tone (personal journals, news, businesses, etc.)
( Internet ) An individual post to a blog.
examples: This blog was originally posted on my personal site but is reproduced on the forums for greater visibility.
